## Using this library

Include this chart as a dependency in your `Chart.yaml` e.g.

### Helm Registry

```yaml
# Chart.yaml
dependencies:
  - name: common
    version: {{template "chart.version" .}}
    repository: {{template "custom.helm.url"}}
```

### OCI

```yaml
# Chart.yaml
dependencies:
  - name: common
    version: {{template "chart.version" .}}
    repository: {{template "custom.helm.oci"}}
```

For more information, take a look at the [Docs](https://TilloTech.github.io/tillo-platform-helm-library/docs/common-library/introduction/).

